{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/extras/SteamStoreDesc1-crop-mini.png?t=1738101522\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One or two players.  Use a mouse or trackpad, keyboard (including Touch Bar), or 1-2 game controllers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Steam version works on Mac (available for mobile and TV elsewhere); updated with support for all recent Mac hardware.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201c<strong>Celtreos</strong>\u201d is like the space shooters of decades past: tiny ship, big weapons, waves of foes, power-ups and obstacles. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Music, Sound and Voice</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 30 different songs (over 45 minutes of music!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can even <strong>play your own music</strong> and auto-next-song for key game events</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stages</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 13 stages: a city, space station, ocean and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Horizontal scrolling but more than one \u201cscreen\u201d of vertical space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Start from any stage you want!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each stage ends with a challenging boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Wall layouts and spawn patterns are partially randomized </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Weapon Arrays, Special Moves, Power-Ups and More</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/extras/SteamGuide-weapons-mini.png?t=1738101522\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose from a huge arsenal of weapons and special abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7 different ships to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize ship properties, such as gun mount locations and top speed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In-game power-ups with weapons, defenses and temporary powers (like Rapid Fire)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Power-down orbs with temporary inconveniences (like Weapon Freeze)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Additional Configuration Options</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Set number of lives, and number of times that special abilities can be used</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play in a window or in Full\u00a0Screen, and specify how much of the display to use in Full\u00a0Screen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set graphics quality to one of three levels</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738101522","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/page.bg.jpg?t=1738101522","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/2734546e52326cc6ba2f50a193ee65695894efdf/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738101522","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/2734546e52326cc6ba2f50a193ee65695894efdf/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738101522","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":1140560,"description":"Try a few free stages!  Updated for macOS 11 \u201cBig Sur\u201d."}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065900/extras/SteamStoreDesc1-crop-mini.png?t=1738101522\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One or two players.  Use